    "abstract": [
        {
            "text": "Emergence of coronavirus disease 2019 pandemic has had its effects on many aspects of life. The practice of oral and maxillofacial radiology has also been affected by the ongoing pandemic. This letter to editor highlights some of the challenges of oral and maxillofacial radiology during this era.",
            "cite_spans": [],
            "ref_spans": [],
            "section": "Abstract"
        },
        {
            "text": "Publisher's Note Springer Nature remains neutral with regard to jurisdictional claims in published maps and institutional affiliations.",
            "cite_spans": [],
